<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="02 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我有一直在想，<delay8 />如果我變成職業運動員的話，<delay20 />
要選哪個運動比較好啊？</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0x3 0x4 0x5" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />假如選足球的話<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
我覺得我應該<delay8 />
會是一位傑出的運動員！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />先是從側邊開始盤球，<delay20 />
接著直接起腳<delay20 />射門破網！<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最後帥氣地把球衣脫掉，<delay8 />
露出腹肌做出慶祝的動作！<delay frames="40" />
我想觀眾們一定會<delay8 />為我瘋狂的──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />假如選棒球的話<tag a="110" b="0" />
我覺得我應該<delay8 />
會是一位傑出的運動員！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽著觀眾席上的熱情加油聲，<delay20 />
打出一支足以<delay8 />
飛出球場的超級全壘打！<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最後還要在跑回本壘的時候，<delay8 />
把球衣脫掉露出腹肌！<delay frames="40" />
我想觀眾們一定會<delay8 />為我瘋狂的──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />假如選籃球的話<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
我覺得我應該<delay8 />
會是一位傑出的運動員！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以在球隊分數落後的時候，<delay20 />
投進逆轉比分的三分球！<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最後在進球之後就把衣服脫掉，<delay20 />
露出腹肌做出慶祝動作！<delay frames="40" />
我想觀眾<delay8 />一定會為我瘋狂的──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0xa 0xb 0xc" /></message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我試著去想了<delay20 />
基於<tag a="110" b="10" />式運動工學<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />設計出來的衣服會是什麼樣子。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />經過反覆思考後，<delay20 />
得出來的結論就是……<delay20 />
印有結實肌肉的T恤──！<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不論是誰，只要穿上它<delay20 />
都可以擁有一身肌肉，<delay20 />
就像是美夢成真，對吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽說跑步的時候，<delay20 />
戴上跑者專用的袖套，<delay8 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以減少肌肉的晃動喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊啊！<delay frames="40" />
<colour id="4" /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果只戴袖套<delay20 />
就去跑步的話<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak />不只手臂可以輕鬆擺動，<delay20 />
大家應該還會一直看我的腹肌吧<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 /><colour id="65535" />
<anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay frames="40" /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒事啦，我在自言自語而已！</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />我一直在想，<delay20 />
有什麼運動服<delay20 />
可以展現我全身的肌肉<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />經過我四處尋找，<delay20 />
終於找到了<delay8 />
游泳用的三角褲！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是我游泳的時候，<delay8 />
都需要用泳圈<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣肌肉不就都被擋住了嗎──！</message>
	<message label="016" attrib="11 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的腦袋裡，<delay20 />
有著一大堆<delay8 />運動相關的知識！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />現在可以破例告訴你喔！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="017" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="2" arg="0x12 0x13 0x14 0x15" /></message>
	<message label="018" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你不覺得穿上劍道的護具，<delay20 />
看起來就會變得很帥氣嗎？<10_4 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那是因為對戰者的決心讓人有這種感覺的。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過護具裡面<delay8 />
味道還滿臭的，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以可能還需要另一種決心就是了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="019" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />原來游泳姿勢的自由式，<delay20 />
意思並不是自由自在地<delay8 />
隨便你游啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為有自由兩個字，<delay20 />
所以我在比賽中帶著泳圈去游，<delay20 />
結果我被罵得超慘的──！</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在馬拉松比賽當中持續奔跑，<delay20 />
跑者就會開始感到亢奮的現象，<delay20 />
一般稱作跑者的愉悅感。
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />另外像是<delay20 />肌肉持續痠痛，<delay20 />
身體就會開始感到快樂的現象，<delay20 />
則是會稱作健身的愉悅感。
<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？<delay20 />沒有人會這樣說嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="021" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？<delay20 />你看起來沒什麼興趣啊？<10_4 />
<anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay20 />果然比起口頭敘述，<delay20 />
還是直接活動身體比較好嗎──！<pageBreak /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我懂！<delay20 />我也是，和你說了這些話以後，<delay frames="30" />
已經有點按捺不住想要運動了──！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好──！<delay20 />我要開始囉──！！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="025" attrib="1b 00 00 01 00 00 00 09">我問你，<delay20 />你知道在野外求生當中，<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最重要的東西是什麼嗎？</message>
	<message label="027" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0x1f 0x20 0x21" /></message>
	<message label="031" attrib="22 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要仔細聽好囉？<10_4 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />野外求生當中最需要的<delay20 />
就是經過鍛鍊的「胸大肌」！</message>
	<message label="032" attrib="23 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要仔細聽好囉？<10_4 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />野外求生當中最需要的<delay20 />
就是經過鍛鍊的「肱二頭肌」！</message>
	<message label="033" attrib="24 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要仔細聽好囉？<10_4 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />野外求生當中最需要的<delay20 />
就是經過鍛鍊的「大腿後側肌」！</message>
	<message label="034" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><10_14 arg="20" /><anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你應該也有聽說過<delay20 />
「堅強的意志力來自結實的肉體」<10_4 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這句話吧──！？
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />即使在野外求生，也絕不輕言放棄的心態<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也就是胸部附近的肌肉！<delay20 />
這才是最重要的──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="035" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shaking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />野外求生有時要在嚴峻的自然環境中<delay20 />
帶著重物跑步<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Sneezing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />或是在大浪當中游泳吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以信賴的只有自己的雙手<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也就是手臂的肌肉！<delay frames="40" />
這才是最重要的ー！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="036" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我不是在說吃的後腿肉，<delay20 />
而是指位在大腿後側的<delay8 />
大腿後側肌肉喔──！<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在大自然的世界裡，逃得夠快才能生存！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />也就是腿部的肌肉！<delay frames="40" />
這才是最重要的──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="042" attrib="2b 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實啊，<delay20 />
我剛才想到了很帥的選手宣誓誓詞。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你稍微聽聽看吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="043" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0x2c 0x2d 0x2e" /></message>
	<message label="044" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="10" />，<delay20 />謹代表全體運動員宣誓！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我們不會畏懼<delay20 />明天的肌肉痠痛，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" />並將用盡全力<delay20 />認真參與比賽！<delay frames="30" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />不過<delay20 />這個宣誓誓詞<delay8 />
好像沒有什麼機會<delay20 />可以用到耶！</message>
	<message label="045" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />開心的春天遠足之旅！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />努力到最後一刻的運動會！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />艱辛的馬拉松大賽！<delay frames="30" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦，奇怪了？<delay20 />
總覺得好像不太對耶<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="046" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />我謹代表全體運動員宣誓，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />肌肉痠痛的時候，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />會像個運動家一樣貼貼布的！<delay frames="30" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，這樣行不通<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
宣誓誓詞裡面<delay8 />忘記要提到
「光明正大」了啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>